  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>Sprint across the battlefield</p><p><em><strong>Trigger:</strong></em> A creature ends their turn</p><p><em><strong>Reaction:</strong></em> You immediately move up to your Speed.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Maneuver Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Agile: (1 SP)</strong> You ignore Difficult Terrain during thismovement.</p><p><strong>Disengage: (1 AP) </strong>You gain the benefits of the Disengage Action for the Movement. When you use this Enhancement, you can spend 1 additional SP to gain the benefits of the Full Disengage Action instead.</p><p><strong>Coordinated Movement: (2 SP, Repeatable)</strong> A willing creature of your choice within 1 Space can move without spending its own movement, provided they’re able to move and they end their movement within 1 Space of your destination.</p>",
